<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Thank You - E-Voting System</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 50px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            opacity: 0; /* Initially invisible */
            transform: scale(0.8); /* Initially scaled down */
            animation: fadeInScale 2s forwards; /* Apply the animation */
        }
        p {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        /* Keyframe animation to fade and scale the text */
        @keyframes fadeInScale {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0.8);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }
        .button{
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Thank You for Reaching Out!</h1>
    <p>Your support request has been submitted successfully. You will receive a response within 24 hours.</p>
    <a href="home.html"><button class="button">Return TO Home</button>  </a>
</body>
</html>
